<graph edgedefault="undirected"><node id="NVIDIA">
  <data key="d0">NVIDIA</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">A company that pioneered accelerated computing and has expanded into various computationally intensive fields, including scientific computing, AI, data science, autonomous vehicles, robotics, and digital twin applications. It is a data center scale AI infrastructure company reshaping industries.&lt;SEP&gt;A company with products and services that function on a standalone basis and are involved in contracts with multiple performance obligations.&lt;SEP&gt;NVIDIA is a company that reports its financial data, including revenue and expenses, and has a focus on Compute &amp; Networking and Graphics segments.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f0b30e55c2d2c942c8ef27807467b3d6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3f2ce3a4f3492cdc62d91339c8332500&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-dd5f5a1a7c540b1c8cafe05b35cfd7fb</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1777252930</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Annual Report on Form 10-K">
  <data key="d0">Annual Report on Form 10-K</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">The Annual Report on Form 10-K is a document that includes NVIDIA's Consolidated Financial Statements, related Notes, and other cautionary statements and risks, which is used to provide a comprehensive view of the company's financial condition and operations.&lt;SEP&gt;The Annual Report on Form 10-K is a comprehensive report filed annually by companies to disclose financial performance and other significant information to investors and regulators.&lt;SEP&gt;The Annual Report on Form 10-K is a document that includes Arista's consolidated financial statements and related notes, as well as forward-looking statements about the company's financial condition and results of operations.&lt;SEP&gt;The Annual Report on Form 10-K is a comprehensive report that includes financial statements and other important information about the company's performance and financial health.&lt;SEP&gt;The Annual Report on Form 10-K is a comprehensive report that includes the company's financial statements and disclosures, including information on accounting policies and tax matters.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f0b30e55c2d2c942c8ef27807467b3d6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-91ba0c40d4695fe5428e9f1aaee99693&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2bcf7035b2263b22ce2270c9abedd363&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-88fbdee009d132142f267759b80b8fcd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-860e208223be2b88258c7bc409f5f9bb</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1777263380</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
