<node id="Consolidated Financial Statements">
  <data key="d0">Consolidated Financial Statements</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Financial statements that include NVIDIA's financial data and are part of the Annual Report on Form 10-K.&lt;SEP&gt;The Consolidated Financial Statements are a comprehensive compilation of the company's financial data, including various notes that provide detailed information on different aspects of the company's financial health.&lt;SEP&gt;Consolidated Financial Statements are financial reports included in the Form 10-K that provide a comprehensive view of the company's financial position, along with the Notes to Consolidated Financial Statements.&gt;&lt;SEP&gt;The Consolidated Financial Statements are comprehensive financial reports that include detailed notes on the company's credit facilities and debt.&lt;SEP&gt;The Consolidated Financial Statements are a comprehensive report of a company's financial position, including assets, liabilities, equity, income, and expenses. They are based on historical and anticipated results, trends, and various assumptions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f0b30e55c2d2c942c8ef27807467b3d6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-91ba0c40d4695fe5428e9f1aaee99693&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-217dcca296bd42c2a1d26c339d20ff32&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-26fa1d1070f941c3c83605779a2af8f0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f5952f8b9b70d6c7a8ac3693a20d7033&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9c9d9262cc591e5a663ff1343e1ab5b9</data>
