  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Notes that provide additional information related to NVIDIA's Consolidated Financial Statements.&lt;SEP&gt;The Notes to the Consolidated Financial Statements provide further discussion related to borrowing facilities, debt obligations, guarantees, commitments, and contingencies.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f0b30e55c2d2c942c8ef27807467b3d6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3f659a7f219f7f617d5e8dc482fab75d</data>
