<node id="Research and Development">
  <data key="d0">Research and Development</data>
  <data key="d1">activity</data>
  <data key="d2">Research and development expenses for fiscal year 2026 were $18,497 million, showing a 43% increase from the previous year.&lt;SEP&gt;Research and development efforts focused on creating new products and technologies, critical to the company's future success.&lt;SEP&gt;Research and development is a core business function critical for future success, involving significant investment in new products and technology development.&lt;SEP&gt;Research and Development is a category of expenses that increased by 5% for the company in the fiscal year ended March 31, 2025.&lt;SEP&gt;Research and Development refers to the company's policies and activities related to innovation and intellectual property.&lt;SEP&gt;Research and Development expenses are costs incurred in creating new products or improving existing ones.&lt;SEP&gt;Research and development expenses increased by $141.8 million, primarily due to increased personnel costs and new product introduction costs.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-db98b1c09ec551c8a83f9131498334c6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8b7994a7b9c5c9289cc48f3afe48287c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1bd342ebc79b6c8d6a4c0db7019159b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1a917696681899c306badc63ac69b7d7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ca207bb382651453029b45cb72e9feff&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5b11abf58ed4d75a128d8d943d08096f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-69f1af12f4eafcde14c51426aec9aa50</data>
