<node id="Interest Income">
  <data key="d0">Interest Income</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Interest income for fiscal year 2026 was $2,300 million, showing an increase from the previous year.&lt;SEP&gt;Interest income consists of interest received on cash, cash equivalents, short-term investments, and loans receivable.&lt;SEP&gt;Interest Income is a category that increased by 5% for the company in the fiscal year ended March 31, 2025.&lt;SEP&gt;Interest Income is the revenue generated from interest on investments, loans, or accounts receivable.&lt;SEP&gt;Interest income for the year ended December 31, 2025, was $383.4 million, a 23.3% increase from the previous year, due to higher cash and marketable securities balances.&lt;SEP&gt;Interest income increased by $158.6 million, due to higher cash and marketable securities balances and investment yields.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-db98b1c09ec551c8a83f9131498334c6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8b7994a7b9c5c9289cc48f3afe48287c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1bd342ebc79b6c8d6a4c0db7019159b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5b11abf58ed4d75a128d8d943d08096f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9c17cee8b5d4c0058ad449ca8d769b9a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-69f1af12f4eafcde14c51426aec9aa50</data>
