  <data key="d2">Interest expense for fiscal year 2026 was $(259) million, showing a slight increase from the previous year.&lt;SEP&gt;Interest Expense is the cost of borrowing money, amounting to $69 in 2026 and $64 in 2025.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-db98b1c09ec551c8a83f9131498334c6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f50e3434e5c216500628bf58a9da4be1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-43a8f055527dad4e87136bbd01caf743</data>
