<node id="Revenue">
  <data key="d0">Revenue</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Revenue for fiscal year 2026 was $215.9 billion, showing a 65% increase from the previous year.&lt;SEP&gt;Revenue is a financial metric representing the income generated from business operations, amounting to $7,012 in 2026 and $7,166 in 2025.&lt;SEP&gt;Total revenue for the year ended December 31, 2024, was $7,003.1 million, a 19.5% increase from the previous year.&lt;SEP&gt;Revenue is a financial metric that represents the total income generated from the company's operations, which increased to $9,005.7 million in 2025, up by 28.6% from $7,003.1 million in 2024.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-fe1fafd9b0c6f09af84ad373757a9b00&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-43a8f055527dad4e87136bbd01caf743&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9c17cee8b5d4c0058ad449ca8d769b9a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9bbc7bb48e6d4943b055b0203ce8adb4</data>
