<node id="United States">
  <data key="d0">United States</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">The United States is a significant economic and political entity with a substantial impact on global trade and business. It serves as a base for many of NVIDIA's direct customers, contributing to 31% of the company's total revenue in fiscal year 2026. Additionally, the United States contributed an 11% share to the net revenue of a company in 2025. The country is also a primary location for companies like AMAT to conduct product development and manufacturing activities.

The United States engages in global trade and has implemented various trade policies and export regulations that affect businesses. Its trade policies, including tariffs, have a direct impact on the business landscape, with a considerable number of customers and suppliers located outside the country. Furthermore, the United States is a potential adopter of laws and regulations related to AI, which may influence the use of AI in product development.

The country is a jurisdiction where companies are subject to income taxes, and tax laws can significantly impact their tax liabilities. Companies operating in the United States are also subject to a range of laws and regulations, including those related to financial disclosures, securities, and corporate governance. Overall, the United States plays a crucial role in the global economy and business operations, with its policies and regulations having far-reaching implications.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dd5f5a1a7c540b1c8cafe05b35cfd7fb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f50e3434e5c216500628bf58a9da4be1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-26fa1d1070f941c3c83605779a2af8f0&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7200d8553fd2e4a1586cd2f8af4129fc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-99b76900a97d7c959bc5ca885c3601da&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-625ca1cf50e3b24380c8601c96bdd7a3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-85c73190292489fe36964fdd5fc32b0c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5d99a02cc7061af948a4068d7dfaf580&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1b0f36135b3b08cac0302bf342d7918d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7d8ee469fd420dd945b64b580faff532</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1777260122</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Blackwell Full-Scale Datacenter Solutions">
  <data key="d0">Blackwell Full-Scale Datacenter Solutions</data>
  <data key="d1">artifact</data>
  <data key="d2">The Blackwell full-scale datacenter solutions represent a new product line from NVIDIA, contributing to a change in their business model and affecting gross margins.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-dd5f5a1a7c540b1c8cafe05b35cfd7fb</data>
