  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Unrecognized Tax Benefits of $4.0 billion include related interest and penalties of $374 million, recorded in non-current income tax payable at the end of fiscal year 2026.&lt;SEP&gt;The Unrecognized Tax Benefits with a gross liability of $452 million as of October 26, 2025, are not expected to result in payment of cash within one year.&lt;SEP&gt;Unrecognized Tax Benefits are potential tax positions that the company has not yet recognized in financial statements due to uncertainties regarding tax audits and outcomes.</data>
