<node id="Income Taxes">
  <data key="d0">Income Taxes</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3f2ce3a4f3492cdc62d91339c8332500&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3f659a7f219f7f617d5e8dc482fab75d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2bcf7035b2263b22ce2270c9abedd363&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9c17cee8b5d4c0058ad449ca8d769b9a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9c9d9262cc591e5a663ff1343e1ab5b9</data>
  <data key="d2">Deferred Tax Assets and Liabilities are part of the company's income tax calculations in the U.S. and foreign jurisdictions.&lt;SEP&gt;Income Taxes are a concept referring to the taxes that the company must pay to the U.S. and foreign jurisdictions based on its income.</data>
