<node id="Semiconductor Systems Segment">
  <data key="d0">Semiconductor Systems Segment</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The Semiconductor Systems segment is a part of a company that will take over the 200mm equipment business from the AGS segment starting in the first quarter of fiscal 2026.&lt;SEP&gt;The Semiconductor Systems segment is a part of a company that contributes significantly to the net revenue, representing the largest share.&gt;&lt;SEP&gt;The Semiconductor Systems segment is a part of the company that derives a significant portion of the company's net revenue and profitability from the sale of equipment used to fabricate semiconductor chips.</data>
