  <data key="d2">U.S. semiconductor technology is subject to export regulations that affect its sale or provision to customers in China.&lt;SEP&gt;U.S. Semiconductor Technology refers to the technology and products developed in the United States for the semiconductor industry.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-e7481c513c84b894dbf5566a03c9c31d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-85c73190292489fe36964fdd5fc32b0c</data>
