  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">The Organization for Economic Cooperation and Development Base Erosion and Profit Shifting Project is a reference to global minimum tax regimes being implemented by various countries where the company does business.&lt;SEP&gt;The Organization for Economic Cooperation and Development Base Erosion and Profit Shifting Project is an initiative that has led to the implementation of global minimum tax regimes in various countries where the organization operates.</data>
