<node id="Singapore">
  <data key="d0">Singapore</data>
  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Singapore is a country where the company has been granted additional conditional reduced tax rates expiring beginning in fiscal 2030.&lt;SEP&gt;Singapore is a country where the company has been granted additional conditional reduced tax rates, which are set to expire beginning in fiscal 2030.&lt;SEP&gt;Singapore is a location where the organization has been granted conditional reduced tax rates, which are set to expire beginning in fiscal 2030.&lt;SEP&gt;Singapore is a location where Applied Materials, Inc. has operations affected by new tax incentive agreements, impacting the company's income tax provisions.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-217dcca296bd42c2a1d26c339d20ff32&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3f659a7f219f7f617d5e8dc482fab75d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7200d8553fd2e4a1586cd2f8af4129fc&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3a29194982b15aafff922b31789e91ea</data>
