<node id="U.S. Government">
  <data key="d0">U.S. Government</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">The U.S. government is responsible for enacting legislations such as the Tax Cuts and Jobs Act, the U.S. CHIPS and Science Act, and the One Big Beautiful Bill Act.&lt;SEP&gt;The U.S. Government is responsible for formulating and implementing trade policies and export regulations.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-217dcca296bd42c2a1d26c339d20ff32&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-85c73190292489fe36964fdd5fc32b0c</data>
