<node id="Effective Tax Rate">
  <data key="d0">Effective Tax Rate</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f50e3434e5c216500628bf58a9da4be1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5b11abf58ed4d75a128d8d943d08096f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9c17cee8b5d4c0058ad449ca8d769b9a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-69f1af12f4eafcde14c51426aec9aa50</data>
  <data key="d2">The effective tax rate for fiscal 2025 was higher than the prior fiscal year primarily due to a remeasurement of deferred tax assets resulting from new tax incentive agreements in Singapore.&gt;&lt;SEP&gt;The effective tax rate is a percentage that decreased for the company in the fiscal year ended March 31, 2025, due to tax benefits from windfall gains and research tax credits.&lt;SEP&gt;The effective tax rate for the year ended December 31, 2025, was 17.4%, an increase from 12.6% in the previous year.&lt;SEP&gt;The effective tax rate decreased from 13.8% in 2023 to 12.6% in 2024.</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1777263379</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
