  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1777259233</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Provision for Income Taxes">
  <data key="d0">Provision for Income Taxes</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f50e3434e5c216500628bf58a9da4be1&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-43a8f055527dad4e87136bbd01caf743&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9c17cee8b5d4c0058ad449ca8d769b9a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-69f1af12f4eafcde14c51426aec9aa50</data>
  <data key="d2">The provision for income taxes and effective tax rates are affected by the geographical composition of pre-tax income, which includes jurisdictions with differing tax rates.&gt;&lt;SEP&gt;Provision for Income Taxes is the amount set aside for income tax payments, amounting to $302 in 2026 and $934 in 2025.&lt;SEP&gt;Provision for income taxes for the year ended December 31, 2025, was $738.3 million, an increase of 78.8% from the previous year.&lt;SEP&gt;The provision for income taxes increased by $78.3 million, partly offset by a decrease in the effective tax rate.</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
