  <data key="d1">location</data>
  <data key="d2">Foreign Jurisdictions are locations outside the United States where the company is also subject to income taxes and changing tax laws.&lt;SEP&gt;Foreign Jurisdictions are locations outside the U.S. where the company is also subject to income taxes and faces tax uncertainties.</data>
