  <data key="d0">Intellectual Property Rights</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Intellectual property rights are legal rights that protect creations of the mind, and their protection is crucial for the company and its customers.&lt;SEP&gt;Intellectual property rights, including patents, trade secrets, copyrights, are vital for protecting technology and are subject to infringement risks.&lt;SEP&gt;Intellectual Property Rights refer to the company's ability to obtain and protect key technologies, which is crucial for its operations and competitive advantage.</data>
