  <data key="d0">Divestitures</data>
  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">Divestitures are the selling of a subsidiary or other business unit, which can be associated with risks such as the inability to complete proposed transactions timely or at all.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-158df076948257685462bdd5a2ffcd95</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1777260109</data>
