<node id="Applied Materials, Inc.">
  <data key="d0">Applied Materials, Inc.</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Applied Materials, Inc. is a company that reported its first quarter financial results, showing revenue of $7.01 billion and various performance metrics such as gross margins and EPS. The company is also involved in the development of new technologies and has received awards for its contributions.&lt;SEP&gt;Applied Materials, Inc. is a company that provides financial outlooks, reports on segment information, and uses non-GAAP financial measures for operational and financial performance evaluation.&lt;SEP&gt;Applied Materials, Inc. is a leader in materials engineering solutions, essential for semiconductor and advanced display technologies.&lt;SEP&gt;Applied Materials, Inc. is a company that provides unaudited reconciliation of GAAP to Non-GAAP results, with details on earnings, income, and various financial adjustments.&lt;SEP&gt;Applied Materials, Inc. is a company that provides unaudited reconciliation of GAAP to Non-GAAP results and financial data.&lt;SEP&gt;Applied Materials, Inc. is the company reporting the financial data, including cash flows, revenue by geography, and non-GAAP reconciliation.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-531a2d4da0efcbaa075b41456e2d3536&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a1e351045874ef4f72c98449caf3e612&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b33403642cf163673735a8236b77616c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c2955967583e4d17eefb4b391be0c469&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-28d0d279e198946ca35e2e93f3701350&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3a29194982b15aafff922b31789e91ea</data>
