  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">GAAP stands for Generally Accepted Accounting Principles, which is the standard used by Applied Materials, Inc. for reporting its financial results.&lt;SEP&gt;GAAP stands for Generally Accepted Accounting Principles, which is a set of accounting standards used for financial reporting and calculations.&lt;SEP&gt;GAAP refers to Generally Accepted Accounting Principles, which is a set of accounting standards used for financial reporting.&lt;SEP&gt;GAAP refers to Generally Accepted Accounting Principles, the standard for accounting practices followed by the company.&lt;SEP&gt;GAAP refers to Generally Accepted Accounting Principles, which are a set of standardized accounting rules and guidelines used for financial reporting in the U.S.&lt;SEP&gt;GAAP stands for Generally Accepted Accounting Principles, which指导the Company's accounting practices, including deferred taxes.&gt;</data>
