<node id="AMD">
  <data key="d0">AMD</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">AMD is a technology company that announced a strategic partnership with Meta to deploy AI infrastructure and accelerate AI model development. They are involved in the production of GPUs, CPUs, and AI systems.&lt;SEP&gt;AMD is a company that drives innovation in high-performance and AI computing, providing full-stack AI solutions and powering billions of experiences across various platforms. It is also involved in a strategic partnership with Meta and is expected to deploy large-scale AI deployments.&lt;SEP&gt;AMD is a company that faces various business impacts due to climate change, government regulations, and other factors.&lt;SEP&gt;AMD is a company that has an approved stock repurchase program and is subject to the Inflation Reduction Act of 2022. It is also subject to Rule 16a-1(f) under the Securities Exchange Act of 1934, as amended.&lt;SEP&gt;AMD is a company that has an approved stock repurchase program and is subject to the Inflation Reduction Act of 2022. It is also subject to Rule 16a-1(f) under the Securities Exchange Act of 1934, as amended.&lt;SEP&gt;AMD is a company that has an approved stock repurchase program and is subject to the Inflation Reduction Act of 2022. It is also involved in Rule 10b5-1 trading plans.&lt;SEP&gt;AMD is a company with a stock repurchase program and is subject to the Inflation Reduction Act of 2022. It is also involved in Rule 10b5-1 trading plans by its executives.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-37167a4c5fea4d3bbb9cfc35f6a693ab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-737963f5a4aa4c7ac5ff75bd66cabe60&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3d5354b5fb76e945ee44e3cc730cae08&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bde81dfa7c0130867695a7023e89cf63&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b0a83ce1ab52e2df80576ef179eeec72&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-42b87cf93df46f504c0e370bbcbc6d94&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-54b2dd7afb5853f7b9fcb8fff6544b20</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
