  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Meta">
  <data key="d0">Meta</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Meta is a company partnering with AMD to scale AI infrastructure, accelerate AI model deployment, and diversify their compute resources.&lt;SEP&gt;Meta is a company building the future of human connection through artificial intelligence and immersive technologies. It launched in 2004 and operates apps like Messenger, Instagram, and WhatsApp. Meta is also involved in a strategic partnership with AMD.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-37167a4c5fea4d3bbb9cfc35f6a693ab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-3d5354b5fb76e945ee44e3cc730cae08</data>
