<node id="Selling, General and Administrative Expenses">
  <data key="d0">Selling, General and Administrative Expenses</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Selling, general and administrative expenses include employee-related expenses in sales, marketing, and administrative functions, along with other corporate-related costs.&lt;SEP&gt;Selling, General and Administrative Expenses is a category of expenses that remained relatively flat for the company in the fiscal year ended March 31, 2025.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8b7994a7b9c5c9289cc48f3afe48287c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5b11abf58ed4d75a128d8d943d08096f</data>
