<node id="Disposal, Restructuring and Other Operating Expenses">
  <data key="d0">Disposal, Restructuring and Other Operating Expenses</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Disposal, restructuring and other operating expenses include transaction costs, employee termination benefits, and contract termination costs.&lt;SEP&gt;Disposal, Restructuring and Other Operating Expenses is a category of expenses that were non-existent in the fiscal year ended March 31, 2025, after being present in the previous fiscal year.&lt;SEP&gt;Disposal, Restructuring and Other Operating Expenses include one-time costs associated with restructuring the company or disposing of assets.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8b7994a7b9c5c9289cc48f3afe48287c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1bd342ebc79b6c8d6a4c0db7019159b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5b11abf58ed4d75a128d8d943d08096f</data>
