  <data key="d0">Impairment of Long-Lived Assets</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Impairment of long-lived assets involves recognizing losses on property, equipment, and intangibles due to lower than anticipated operating results.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-8b7994a7b9c5c9289cc48f3afe48287c</data>
