  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">March 31, 2025, is the end date of the fiscal year for which the Company reported its financial statements and operations.&gt;&lt;SEP&gt;March 31, 2025 is the fiscal year end date mentioned in the context of financial activities and obligations.&lt;SEP&gt;March 31, 2025 is the fiscal year-end date when the Company completed its annual goodwill impairment test.&gt;</data>
