  <data key="d0">Assessment of contract combination criteria</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">The Assessment of contract combination criteria is a process used to determine if multiple contracts with the same customer should be treated as a single contract for accounting purposes.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-f5952f8b9b70d6c7a8ac3693a20d7033</data>
