  <data key="d0">Valuation of Equity Investments Measured at Fair Value</data>
  <data key="d1">method</data>
  <data key="d2">The Valuation of Equity Investments Measured at Fair Value is a method used to estimate the fair value of non-marketable securities, which can include investments in early-stage development enterprises.</data>
