  <data key="d0">Non-marketable securities</data>
  <data key="d1">financialdata</data>
  <data key="d2">Non-marketable securities are investments in unlisted or early-stage companies, which may be valued using the NAV practical expedient, representing the estimated fair value of these investments.</data>
